1. e4 c6 2. Nc3 d5 3. Nf3 dxe4 4. Nxe4 Nd7 5. d4 Ngf6 6. Ng3 e6 7. Bd3 Be7 8. O-O O-O 9. Qe2 c5 10. Rd1 Qc7 (10... cxd4 11. Nxd4 Nc5 12. b3 Nxd3 13. Rxd3 Bd7 14. Bb2 $16 Qc7 15. Rad1 Bc6 16. Nxc6 bxc6 17. Ne4 $16) 11. Bg5 b6 { big mistake in fact - not prioritising king safety } { [%cal Gb7b6] } (11... cxd4 12. Ne4 h6 13. Bh4 Nd5 14. Bxe7 Nxe7 15. Nxd4 Ne5 $10) 12. d5 Nxd5 (12... exd5 13. Qxe7 Re8 14. Bxh7+ (14. Bxf6 Rxe7 15. Bxe7 $16) 14... Kxh7 15. Qxf7 Rf8 16. Qe6 $16) 13. Bxe7 Nxe7 14. Bxh7+ Kxh7 15. Ng5+ (15. Rxd7 Bxd7 16. Ng5+ $16 { move order also works }) 15... Kg8 16. Rxd7 (16. Qh5 Nf6 17. Qe2 Bb7 $17) 16... Qxd7 17. Qh5 Rd8 18. Qxf7+ Kh8 19. h4 { inaccuracy } (19. Re1 Qe8 (19... Qd1 20. Rxd1 Rxd1+ 21. Nf1 $16) 20. Nh5 Qg8 (20... Qxf7 21. Nxf7+ Kg8 22. Nxd8 $16) 21. Qxe7 $16) (19. Nh5 Qd1+ 20. Rxd1 Rxd1#) 19... Qe8 20. Nh5 Qf8 { the big mistake } (20... Qxf7 { is essential for black to play } 21. Nxf7+ Kg8 22. Nxd8 Bd7 23. Nb7 Bc6 24. Nd6 (24. Ng3 Bxb7 $17) 24... Rd8 25. Nc4 Ng6 $10) 21. Nf6 Ng8 22. Qh5+ Nh6 23. Qg6 (23. Nf7+ { would be a mistake } 23... Qxf7 $17) 23... gxf6 24. Qh7# { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0


