1. d4 (1. g3 c5 2. c4 g6) 1... d5 2. Nf3 e6 3. e3 c5 4. c4 Nc6 5. Nc3 Nf6 6. dxc5 { not respecting tempo - not waiting for bishop to make it move again } (6. cxd5 exd5 7. Be2 (7. Bb5 cxd4 8. Nxd4 Bd7 9. O-O $10) 7... c4 8. O-O $10) (6. a3 dxc4 (6... a6 7. dxc5 (7. b3 cxd4 8. exd4 Be7 9. Be2 $10) 7... Bxc5 8. b4 Bd6 9. cxd5 exd5 10. Be2 $14) 7. Bxc4 a6 8. O-O b5 9. Bd3 cxd4 10. exd4 Be7 $10) 6... Bxc5 7. a3 a6 8. b4 Bd6 (8... Ba7 9. Bb2 O-O 10. Qc2 $14 Qe7 11. Rd1 $14) 9. Bb2 (9. cxd5 exd5 10. Be2 $14 (10. Nxd5 Nxd5 11. Qxd5 Bxb4+ 12. axb4 Qxd5 $17)) 9... O-O 10. Qd2 { inaccuracy } (10. cxd5 exd5 11. Be2 Be6 $14 12. O-O Rc8 13. Rc1 $10) 10... Qe7 11. Bd3 { mistake } (11. cxd5 exd5 12. Be2 $10 (12. Nxd5 Nxd5 13. Qxd5 Rd8 (13... Be6 14. Qd2 Rac8 15. Bc3 Bg4 16. Be2 Rfd8 17. Qb2 Bxf3 18. Bxf3 $14) 14. Qb3 (14. Qh5 Bxb4+ 15. axb4 Qxb4+ 16. Ke2 Qxb2+ 17. Nd2 Rxd2+ $17) 14... Ne5 $10 15. Nxe5 Bxe5 16. Bxe5 Qxe5 17. Rc1 $10)) 11... dxc4 12. Bxc4 b5 13. Bd3 Rd8 14. Qe2 { inaccuracy } (14. O-O Bb7 15. Rfd1 Ne5 16. Nxe5 Bxe5 17. h3 Rac8 $15) 14... Bb7 { symmetrical position but White is a move behind } 15. O-O Ne5 { King safety centric use of lead in development - attacking defensive knight on f3 } (15... h6 16. Ne4 $10) 16. Nxe5 Bxe5 17. f4 { creates weaknesses around White king } (17. Rfd1 Rac8 18. Rac1 Bb8 19. h3 h6 20. Bb1 Rxd1+ 21. Rxd1 Qc7 22. g3 h5 23. Rc1 Qb6 24. Rc2 Rc4 25. Ba2 Rc7 26. Qd1 Qc6 27. e4 Nxe4 28. Nd5 Qxc2 29. Ne7+ Rxe7 30. Qxc2 Rd7 $17) 17... Bc7 18. e4 { even more King safety issues created - White King escape squares becoming limited } (18. h3 e5 19. Rad1 Re8 $17 20. a4 exf4 21. axb5 fxe3 $17) 18... Rac8 19. e5 { makes things even worse - even more King safety issues emerging } 19... Bb6+ 20. Kh1 Ng4 (20... Nd5 21. Nxd5 Bxd5 $17) 21. Be4 (21. Qxg4 Rxd3 22. Rac1 (22. Ne2 Rc2 23. f5 h5 24. f6 Qf8 25. Qg5 Rxe2 $17) 22... Qd7 23. Rcd1 Rd2 24. h3 h5 25. Qg3 Rxc3 26. Bxc3 Rxd1 $17) (21. Bxh7+ Kxh7 22. Qxg4 Rd2 23. Rf3 (23. Bc1 Bxg2+ 24. Qxg2 Rxg2 25. Kxg2 Rxc3 $17) 23... Bxf3 24. Qxf3 Rxb2 $17) 21... Qh4 (21... Nxh2 22. Bxb7 Nxf1 23. Qg4 Ne3 24. Qf3 Qh4+ 25. Qh3 Qxf4 26. Bxc8 Ng4 27. Ne4 Rd3 28. Qh5 Rf3 29. Nd2 Rh3+ 30. Qxh3 Nf2+ 31. Kg1 Nxh3+ 32. Kh1 Nf2+ 33. Kg1 Ng4+ 34. Bd4 Bxd4+ 35. Kh1 Qh2#) 22. g3 (22. h3 Rxc3 23. Bxc3 (23. Qxg4 Rxh3+ 24. Qxh3 Qxh3+ 25. gxh3 Bxe4+ 26. Kh2 Rd2+ 27. Kg3 Rg2+ 28. Kh4 Bd8+ 29. Kh5 Bg6#) 23... Bxe4 24. Qxe4 Qg3 25. hxg4 Qh4#) 22... Rxc3 23. gxh4 (23. Bxb7 Rxg3 24. Rac1 Re3 (24... Rh3 25. Rc2 Re3 26. Qg2 Re1 { threat of Nxh2 } 27. Bc3 Red1 28. Bf3 (28. Rc1 Rxc1 29. Rxc1 Nf2+ 30. Kg1 Nd3+ 31. Kh1 Nxc1 $17) 28... Nxh2 29. Qxh2 Rxf1+ 30. Kg2 Rf2+ 31. Rxf2 Qxf2+ 32. Kh3 Qxf3+ $17) 25. Qg2 Rh3 26. Rc2 Ne3 27. Qf2 Nxf1 28. Qxh4 Rxh4 $17) 23... Rd2 (23... Rh3 { is a bad blunder and white wins } 24. Bxb7 Rxh2+ 25. Qxh2 Nxh2 26. Kxh2 $16) (23... Re3 { only draws } 24. Qxe3 (24. Qxg4 Bxe4+ 25. Kg1 (25. Qg2 Bxg2+ 26. Kxg2 Re2+ 27. Kf3 Rxb2 $17) 25... Rg3#) 24... Bxe3 25. Bxb7 Rd2 26. Bg2 Rxb2 $10) 24. Qxd2 (24. Qe1 Rxh2#) (24. Rfe1 Bxe4+ 25. Qg2 Bxg2#) 24... Bxe4+ 25. Qg2 Rh3 { end of game } 26. Bd4 (26. Qxe4 Rxh2#) 26... Bxd4 27. Rf2 Bxf2 28. a4 Rxh2# { 0 } 0-1


