1. e4 e6 2. d4 d5 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. exd5 Nxd5 5. Nf3 c5 { inaccuracy } (5... Be7 6. Bd3 Nxc3 7. bxc3 Nd7 8. Qe2 Nf6 $14) 6. Nxd5 Qxd5 (6... exd5 7. Bb5+ Bd7 8. Bxd7+ Qxd7 9. O-O Be7 10. dxc5 Bxc5 11. Re1+ Be7 12. Ne5 Qd8 13. Bg5 f6 (13... Bxg5 14. Nc6+ Qe7 15. Rxe7+ Bxe7 16. Nxe7 $16) 14. Qh5+ g6 15. Nxg6 hxg6 16. Qxh8+ Kd7 17. Qh3+ Kc7 18. Bf4+ Bd6 19. Bxd6+ Qxd6 20. Re8 $16) 7. Be3 cxd4 8. Nxd4 a6 9. Be2 Qxg2 { makes things worse } (9... e5 10. Nf3 (10. Bf3 Qa5+ { seems the absolute safest way for black to play here } (10... Qd8 11. Nb3 Qxd1+ 12. Rxd1 $14) (10... e4 11. Nb3 Qf5 12. Be2 $14) 11. Bd2 Qc7 $10 12. Qe2 Be7 13. Nb3 Nc6 $14) 10... Qxd1+ 11. Rxd1 Nc6 $14) 10. Bf3 Qg6 11. Qd2 e5 12. O-O-O (12. Nb3 Be7 13. O-O-O Qf5 14. Bd5 Nc6 { way of losing most of the advantage - white only slightly better if anything }) 12... exd4 (12... Be7 13. Rhg1 Qd6 (13... Qf6 14. Bg5 Qd6 15. Bxe7 Qxe7 16. Bxb7 Bxb7 (16... Qxb7 17. Ne6 (17. Nf5 O-O 18. Qh6 f6 19. Rxg7+ Qxg7 20. Qxg7#) 17... Qe7 18. Nxg7+ $16) 17. Nf5 Qf6 18. Nxg7+ Kf8 19. Qb4+ Qe7 20. Rd8#) 14. Nf5 Qxd2+ (14... Qc7 15. Nxg7+ Kf8 16. Bh6 $16) 15. Rxd2 Bxf5 16. Bxb7 O-O 17. Bxa8 $16) 13. Bxd4 Nc6 14. Bf6 { [%cal Gd4f6,Gd2d8,Gf3c6] } (14. Bxg7 Bxg7 15. Bxc6+ bxc6 16. Qd8#) 14... Qxf6 (14... Be7 15. Bxc6+ bxc6 16. Qd8+ Bxd8 17. Rxd8#) 15. Rhe1+ Be7 16. Bxc6+ Kf8 (16... bxc6 17. Qd8#) 17. Qd8+ Bxd8 18. Re8# { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0


