1. e4 c5 2. d4 cxd4 3. c3 d3?! { B21 Sicilian Defense: Smith-Morra Gambit Declined, Push Variation } { (-0.26 → 0.63) Inaccuracy. dxc3 was best. } (3... dxc3 4. Nxc3 Nc6 5. Nf3 e6 6. Be2 Qc7 7. O-O Nf6 8. Qa4) 4. Bxd3 d6 5. Nf3?! { (0.81 → 0.13) Inaccuracy. Ne2 was best. } (5. Ne2 Nc6 6. c4 Nf6 7. O-O Ne5 8. b3 a6 9. Nbc3 e6) 5... Nd7?! { (0.13 → 0.84) Inaccuracy. Nf6 was best. } (5... Nf6 6. Bc2 Qc7 7. a4 g6 8. Na3 a6 9. O-O Bg7 10. Qe2) 6. Nbd2 e6 7. Qe2 Be7 8. c4 Qc7 9. b3 a6 10. Bb2 Bf6 11. Bxf6 Ngxf6 12. O-O O-O 13. Rfe1 Rd8 14. Rad1 Ne5 15. Bb1 Bd7 16. Nd4 Bc6 17. N2f3 Nxf3+ 18. Qxf3 Rac8 19. Rd2 Nd7?! { (0.00 → 0.57) Inaccuracy. b5 was best. } (19... b5 20. cxb5 axb5 21. Qe3 Bd7 22. Red1 e5 23. Nf3 Be6 24. h3 h6 25. b4 d5 26. exd5) 20. Red1 Ne5 21. Qg3 Be8 22. h3 b5 23. cxb5 axb5 24. Kh2 d5?? { (0.65 → 2.40) Blunder. Ng6 was best. } (24... Ng6 25. Ne2 h5 26. f4 Qe7 27. Qe3 h4 28. Nd4 b4 29. Qf2 Rb8 30. Bd3 Rbc8 31. Ne2) 25. f4?! { (2.40 → 1.68) Inaccuracy. Rc2 was best. } (25. Rc2) 25... Ng6 26. e5 Ne7 27. h4 Qc3?! { (1.79 → 2.74) Inaccuracy. Bd7 was best. } (27... Bd7) 28. Rd3 Qb2? { (2.80 → 4.55) Mistake. Qb4 was best. } (28... Qb4) 29. h5 h6?! { (4.10 → 5.28) Inaccuracy. Qa3 was best. } (29... Qa3 30. Qh4) 30. R3d2? { (5.28 → 3.01) Mistake. Qh4 was best. } (30. Qh4 Nc6 31. Nxb5 Nxe5 32. R3d2 Nc4 33. Rxb2 Nxb2 34. Rd2 Bxb5 35. Rxb2 d4 36. f5 exf5) 30... Qc3 31. Rd3 Qb2?? { (2.69 → 5.57) Blunder. Qc5 was best. } (31... Qc5 32. Qh4) 32. Qh4 Rd7 33. Rg3 Rc3 34. Bd3 Rxd3 35. Rdxd3 Kf8 36. Qg4 g6 37. hxg6 Nxg6 38. f5 exf5 39. Qxf5 Qc1?! { (12.87 → Mate in 7) Checkmate is now unavoidable. Kg8 was best. } (39... Kg8 40. Qf6) 40. Rxg6 { Black resigns. } 1-0


