1. e4 c5 2. d4 cxd4 3. c3 dxc3 4. Nxc3 Nc6 5. Nf3 d6 6. Bc4 e6 7. O-O Nf6 8. Qe2 a6 9. Rd1 Qc7 10. Bf4 Ne5 11. Bb3 Be7 12. Rac1 Qb8 13. Nd4 { a beautiful
idea to liberate f pawn } 13... O-O 14. Bg3 Ned7 { mistake - black should try and hold
on to the e5 strongpoint } (14... Bd7 15. f4 Nc6 16. Nc2 (16. f5 Nxd4 17. Rxd4 e5 (17... exf5 18. exf5 Bxf5 (18... Qd8 19. Rcd1 $17) 19. Qxe7 $16) 18. Rdd1) 16... g6 17. f5 gxf5 (17... Re8 18. Ne3 $15) 18. exf5 Kh8 19. fxe6 Bxe6 20. Bxe6 fxe6 21. Qxe6 $16) 15. f4 e5 { big mistake - d5 gaping hole now and
