1. e4 { GM Alan Pichot, Argentina.AKA platyborg - 2377 - became GM in 2016 -
2021 world rank 143 - FIDE 2630 } 1... c5 2. d4 cxd4 3. c3 Nf6 4. Bd3 Nc6 (4... d5 5. e5 Nfd7 (5... Ne4 6. cxd4 Bf5 7. f3 Qa5+ 8. Kf1 Nc6 9. Ne2 Rd8 10. fxe4 dxe4 11. Bc2 $16) (5... Ng8 6. cxd4 Nc6 7. Be3 Nh6 8. Bxh6 gxh6 9. Ne2 Bg4 10. f3 Bh5 11. O-O $16) 6. e6 fxe6 7. Qh5+ g6 8. Bxg6+ (8. Qxg6+ hxg6 9. Bxg6#) 8... hxg6 9. Qxg6#) (4... dxc3 5. Nxc3 d6 6. Nf3 e6 7. Qe2 Nc6 8. O-O $15) 5. f4 d5 6. e5 Ne4 7. Nf3 dxc3 8. Nxc3 Bf5 9. O-O e6 10. Kh1 h5 11. Qe2 Nc5 { mistake } (11... Nxc3 12. bxc3 Bxd3 13. Qxd3 g6 14. Rb1 b6 15. c4 Rc8 16. cxd5 Qxd5 17. Qe2 (17. Qxd5 exd5 18. Rd1 Be7 $15) 17... Nb4) 12. Bxf5 exf5 13. Be3 Ne6 14. Rad1 d4 15. Nb5 Bc5 16. b4 a6 (16... Bxb4 17. Nfxd4 Nexd4 18. Bxd4 O-O (18... Nxd4 19. Rxd4 Qe7 20. Qc4 Bc5 21. Nd6+ Bxd6 22. exd6 $16) 19. Qxh5 $16) 17. bxc5 (17. Nbxd4 Bxd4 18. Nxd4 Ncxd4 19. Bxd4 Nxd4 20. Qb2 Qc7 21. Rxd4 $14) 17... axb5 18. Qxb5 O-O 19. Qxb7 { mistake } (19. Bxd4 Ncxd4 20. Nxd4 Nxd4 21. Qc4 b5 22. Qxd4) 19... Qd5 { big mistake going into self-pin } (19... Qa5 20. Bg1 (20. Qxc6 dxe3 $17) 20... Qa4 $17) 20. Nxd4 Nexd4 21. Rxd4 (21. Bxd4 Rab8 { maybe what the GM had hoped for } 22. Qa6 Nxd4 $17) 21... Qxc5 (21... Rab8 22. Qxb8 Qxd4 23. Qxf8+ Kxf8 24. Bxd4 $16) 22. Rdd1 Qxe3 23. Qxc6 Rxa2 24. Rde1 Qd2 25. e6 fxe6 26. Qxe6+ Kh7 27. Qc6 Rc8 28. Qf3 g6 { huge mistake - the boucy
roads to k are more dangerous now } (28... h4 29. Qh5+ Kg8 30. Qg6 Rf8) 29. Re7+ Kh8 30. Qb7 { setting up killer common squares through battery } 30... Qc3 31. Rh7+ Kg8 32. Qf7# { Black checkmated } 1-0


