1. c4 g6 2. d4 Nf6 3. Nc3 d5 4. Nf3 Bg7 5. e3 O-O 6. Be2 dxc4 (6... c5 7. O-O cxd4 8. exd4 Nc6 9. c5 $10 (9. h3 $10)) 7. Bxc4 c5 8. d5 e6 9. dxe6 Qxd1+ 10. Kxd1 Bxe6 11. Bxe6 fxe6 { [%csl Be6][%cal Be8e4] } 12. Ke2 Nc6 13. Rd1 Rad8 14. Rxd8 Rxd8 15. Ng5 Re8 16. Nge4 { the knight on e4 is unassailable from pawns given absence of blacks d and d5 pawns.Sitting in front of an isolated pawn affords the knight frontal protection } { [%cal Ye8e4] } 16... Nxe4 17. Nxe4 b6 18. Rb1 Nb4 19. Bd2 Nd5 (19... Nxa2 20. Ra1 Nb4 21. Bxb4 cxb4 22. Rxa7 Bxb2 23. Rb7 Bc3 24. Rxb6 h5 25. h3 $16) 20. a4 { restraining blacks queenside pawn majority } 20... Rc8 21. b3 { pawns on light squares away from opponents bishop } { [%csl Bb3,Ba4,Bg7] } 21... Bf8 (21... c4 22. Nd6 Rc5 23. Nxc4 $16) 22. Rc1 Be7 23. b4 c4 24. b5 { [%csl Yc4] } 24... Kf7 (24... Ba3 25. Rc2 c3 26. Bxc3 (26. Nxc3 Nb4 $17) 26... Bb4 27. Kd2 Rc4 28. Bxb4 Rxe4 29. Bd6 Rxa4 30. f3 g5 31. Rc8+ Kf7 32. g3 $14 Kg6 $14 (32... Ra2+ 33. Kd3 Rxh2 34. e4 Nf6 35. Rc7+ Kg6 36. Re7 $16)) 25. Bc3 Ba3 26. Rc2 Nxc3+ (26... Be7 27. Nd2 Bf6 28. Bxf6 Kxf6 29. Rxc4 Rxc4 30. Nxc4 Nc3+ 31. Kd3 Nxa4 32. Kd4 Nc5 { one pawn restrains two - capablanca endgame principle } 33. Nd6 a5 34. bxa6 Nxa6 35. Nc8 b5 36. Nd6 b4 37. Ne4+ Kf5 38. Nd2 g5 39. Kc4 h5 40. Kb5 Nb8 41. Kxb4 $16) 27. Rxc3 Bb4 28. Rc2 Ke7 29. Nd2 c3 30. Ne4 Ba5 31. Kd3 Rd8+ 32. Kc4 Rd1 33. Nxc3 Rh1 34. Ne4 { seems strongest } { [%cal Yc3e4,Bh1h2] } (34. h3 Bxc3 35. Kxc3 Rd1 $16) 34... Rxh2 35. Kd4 Kd7 (35... Rxg2 36. Rc7+ Kd8 37. Rxh7 Kc8 38. Rxa7 Bb4 39. Ke5 Kb8 40. Rd7 Rg1 41. Rd4 Be7 42. Kxe6 $16) 36. g3 Bb4 37. Ke5 Rh5+ 38. Kf6 Be7+ (38... Rf5+ 39. Kg7 Be7 40. g4 Re5 41. Rc4 $16) 39. Kg7 e5 40. Rc6 Rh1 41. Kf7 { not kf8 which botvinnik was trying to claim by forfeiit had been sealed.petrosian hd a peculiar way of writing 7 with tails } 41... Ra1 42. Re6 Bd8 (42... Bb4 43. Nf6+ Kc8 44. Re8+ Kb7 45. Rh8 Rxa4 46. Rxh7 g5 47. Kg6+ Kb8 48. Kxg5 Ra5 49. Ne4 Rxb5 50. g4 Rd5 51. Kf5 a5 52. g5 Rd8 53. g6 Bf8 54. Rh8 Rc8 55. Ke6 a4 56. Nd6 Rd8 57. g7 $16) 43. Rd6+ Kc8 44. Ke8 Bc7 45. Rc6 Rd1 (45... Rxa4 46. Nc3 Ra5 47. Nd5 Rxb5 48. Rxc7+ Kb8 49. e4 Rxd5 50. exd5 Kxc7 51. Ke7 a5 52. d6+ Kc6 53. d7 $16) 46. Ng5 Rd8+ 47. Kf7 Rd7+ 48. Kg8 { end of game } 48... h5 49. Rxg6 Rd2 50. Rc6 Kb7 51. Ne4 Rd1 52. Rh6 Ra1 53. Nc3 a5 54. bxa6+ Kxa6 55. Rxh5 $16 { 1-0 Black resigns. } 1-0


