1. Nc3 { A funny bullet chess game by Magnus Carlsen } 1... e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nb1 Nf6 4. Ng1 d5 5. Nf3 Bc5 6. Ng1 e4 7. e3 O-O 8. d4 exd3 9. cxd3 { Engines suggest -2.85 for black } 9... d4 10. e4 Re8 11. Be2 Nd7 { the position just closed up a lot more } (11... Nxe4 12. dxe4 Rxe4 13. Nf3 (13. Kf1 d3 14. Bf3 Re8 15. Nc3 Nb4 16. Nh3 Bxh3 17. gxh3 Qh4 18. Be3 Bxe3 19. fxe3 Nc2 20. Qxd3 Rxe3 $17) 13... d3 $17) 12. Nf3 Nde5 (12... Bf8 13. Nbd2 a5 14. O-O a4 15. a3 $17) 13. Nxe5 Nxe5 14. O-O { position is equal now } 14... f5 15. f4 Nc6 (15... Nf7 16. Bf3 c6 $14) 16. e5 a5 17. Nd2 Be6 18. a3 a4 19. Bf3 Qd7 20. Kh1 Bf8 (20... Na5 21. Rb1 Qb5 22. Qe2 g6 $17) 21. Rg1 b5 22. g4 fxg4 23. Rxg4 Kh8 (23... Bxg4 24. Bxg4 Qd8 25. Qe2 Ra6 26. Nf3 $16) 24. Rg2 Rab8 25. Be4 Ne7 26. Qh5 Bf5 27. Nf3 Bxe4 (27... g6 28. Ng5 h6 29. Qh4 $16) 28. dxe4 { White is at+4 now } 28... Qc6 29. Ng5 h6 30. Nf7+ Kg8 31. Nxh6+ Kh7 32. Nf7+ Kg8 33. f5 g6 34. Qh8+ Kxf7 35. e6+ { end of game } 35... Qxe6 36. fxe6+ Kxe6 37. Qh3+ Kf7 38. Rf2+ Kg7 39. Bh6+ Kg8 40. Qe6+ Kh7 41. Rf7+ Kxh6 42. Qh3+ Kg5 43. Rg1# { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0


