1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 e6 { On Nc6 Fischer has beaten Mednis with d3 in 1957 encouter. On d6 Fischer has played nearly exclusively d4 normal sicilian variation.Only 2 times Bb5+ and once Nc3 } 3. d3 { Fischer had 6 games here with 83.3% win rate compared to 64.7% win rate over 17 games with d4 } { [%cal Gd2d3] } 3... Nc6 4. g3 g6 5. Bg2 Bg7 6. O-O Nge7 7. Re1 d6 (7... O-O 8. c3 e5 9. a3 d6 10. b4 $10) 8. c3 { Note the greater accuracy - dont always have to have stereotypical knights on d2 and f3 - Fischer is actually "playing the position" here } 8... O-O { inaccuracy } (8... e5 9. a3 O-O 10. b4 a6 11. Nbd2 h6 $10) 9. d4 cxd4 10. cxd4 d5 (10... Qb6 11. d5 Ne5 12. Nxe5 Bxe5 13. Na3 Bd4 14. Be3 Bxe3 15. Rxe3 Qxb2 16. Nc4 Qb4 17. Rc1 exd5 18. Rb3 Qa4 19. exd5 Nf5 20. Qd2 $14) 11. e5 Bd7 12. Nc3 Rc8 13. Bf4 Na5 14. Rc1 b5 15. b3 (15. a3 Nc4 16. Re2 a5 17. h4 h6 18. Bh3 Qb6 $10) 15... b4 16. Ne2 Bb5 17. Qd2 Nac6 18. g4 (18. Bh6 { would be falling into horrible trap } 18... Bxh6 19. Qxh6 Nf5 20. Qd2 Bxe2 21. Qxe2 (21. Rxe2 Ncxd4 22. Nxd4 Rxc1+ 23. Qxc1 Nxd4 24. Re1 Qc8 $17) 21... Ncxd4 22. Nxd4 Nxd4 $17) 18... a5 (18... f6 19. exf6 Rxf6 20. Bg5 Rf8 21. Nf4 e5 22. Nxe5 Qd6 23. Nxc6 Nxc6 24. Ne6 Rfe8 25. Nxg7 $16) 19. Ng3 Qb6 20. h4 Nb8 21. Bh6 Nd7 (21... f6 22. Bxg7 Kxg7 23. exf6+ Rxf6 24. Qg5 { threat of Nh5+ } 24... Rf7 25. Rxc8 Nxc8 26. Ne5 Rf6 (26... Qxd4 27. Nh5+ Kg8 28. Nf6+ Kg7 29. h5 Rxf6 30. h6+ Kf8 31. Qxf6+ Ke8 32. Qh8+ Ke7 33. Nxg6+ hxg6 34. Qxd4 $16) 27. Nh5+ Kg8 28. Qxf6 $16) 22. Qg5 Rxc1 23. Rxc1 Bxh6 24. Qxh6 Rc8 25. Rxc8+ Nxc8 26. h5 Qd8 27. Ng5 Nf8 28. Be4 Qe7 (28... a4 29. hxg6 fxg6 30. Nh5 gxh5 31. Bxh7+ Nxh7 32. Qxh7+ Kf8 33. Qf7#) (28... dxe4 29. N3xe4 Nd6 30. Nf6+ (30. hxg6 Nxe4 (30... hxg6 31. Nxd6 a4 32. Ngxf7 Qe7 33. Qh8#) 31. gxh7+ Kh8 32. Nxf7#) 30... Qxf6 31. exf6 Ne8 32. Ne4 $16) 29. Nxh7 Nxh7 30. hxg6 fxg6 (30... dxe4 31. Qxh7+ Kf8 32. Qh8#) 31. Bxg6 Ng5 (31... Qg7 32. Bxh7+ Kf8 33. Qf4+ Qf7 34. Nh5 Qxf4 35. Nxf4 Bd7 36. Kg2 $16) (31... Nf8 32. Nh5 Nd7 33. g5 a4 34. Nf6+ Nxf6 35. exf6 Qd7 36. f7+ Qxf7 37. Bxf7+ $16) 32. Nh5 Nf3+ 33. Kg2 Nh4+ 34. Kg3 Nxg6 35. Nf6+ (35. Qxg6+ Kf8 36. f4 Qf7 37. Qh6+ Ke7 38. Ng7 Be8 39. f5 $16) 35... Kf7 36. Qh7+ { game ended here } 36... Kf8 37. Qg8# { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0


