1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. O-O Nxe4 5. d4 Be7 { [%cal Be4d6,Bf8e7] } (5... Nd6 6. Bxc6 dxc6 7. dxe5 Nf5 8. Qxd8+ Kxd8 $14) 6. Qe2 (6. dxe5 d5 7. exd6 Nxd6 $14) 6... Nd6 7. Bxc6 bxc6 (7... dxc6 8. dxe5 Nf5 9. Rd1 Bd7 10. Nc3 O-O 11. g4 Nh4 12. Nxh4 Bxh4 13. g5 Bxg5 14. Rxd7 Qxd7 15. Bxg5 $16) 8. dxe5 Nb7 { [%csl Yb7] } 9. b3 (9. Nc3 O-O 10. Nd4 $14) 9... O-O 10. Bb2 d5 11. exd6 (11. c4 Nc5 12. Nd4 $10) 11... cxd6 12. Nbd2 Re8 13. Rfe1 Bd7 14. Ne4 { mistake - white ends up reacting to threats mode after this } { [%cal Yd2e4,Be8e2] } (14. Nf1 d5 15. Qd2 $10 Bf8 16. Ne5 Nd6 17. Ng3 $10) 14... d5 { [%cal Yd5e4] } 15. Ned2 (15. Ng3 Bb4 16. Qd1 Bxe1 $17) (15. Nc3 Ba3 16. Qf1 Bxb2 $17) 15... Ba3 { [%cal Ye8e2,Ya3b2] } 16. Be5 (16. Qa6 Bxb2 17. Rab1 Nc5 18. Rxe8+ Bxe8 19. Qf1 Bf6 $17) 16... f6 { [%cal Yf6e5] } 17. Qa6 { addresses the threat but creating downsides in process } 17... fxe5 { [%cal Yf6e5,Ya3f8] } 18. Qxa3 (18. Qxb7 e4 19. Nd4 (19. Qa6 Bb4 20. Qb7 a5 $17) 19... Bb2 $17) 18... e4 { [%cal Ye4f3] } 19. Nd4 Qf6 { threat Qxd4 } { [%cal Yf6d4] } 20. c3 { weakens d3 } 20... Rf8 { threat Qxf2 check } { [%cal Yf8f2] } 21. f3 { weakens dark squares } (21. Rf1 Qh6 (21... Qg5 22. f4 (22. Qc1 Bh3 23. g3 Bxf1 $15) 22... Rxf4 23. Rxf4 Qxf4 24. Qe7 Qd6 $17) 22. Nb1 e3 23. f3 Qg5 24. b4 Bh3 25. Qb2 c5 26. Nb3 d4 27. cxd4 cxb4 $17) 21... Qg5 { threat Qxd2 } { [%cal Yg5d2,Bd7h3] } 22. Qc1 (22. Nf1 exf3 23. Nxf3 Rxf3 $17) 22... Nc5 { threat Nd3 and Bh3 } { [%cal Yc5d3] } 23. Nf1 Qg6 { threat exf3 } { [%cal Ye4f3] } 24. Re3 Nd3 { threat NxQ } { [%cal Yd3c1] } 25. Qd1 Nf4 { threat Qxg2 check } { [%cal Yg6g2] } 26. Ng3 h5 { threat h4 } { [%cal Yh5h4] } 27. Nde2 Nxg2 { [%cal Yg2e3] } 28. Kxg2 exf3+ { [%cal Yf3g2] } 29. Rxf3 (29. Kh1 h4 30. Ng1 hxg3 31. Nxf3 Qh5 32. Qe2 Bg4 33. Rf1 Rf4 34. Kg1 Raf8 35. hxg3 Rxf3 $17) 29... Bh3+ { [%cal Yh3g2] } 30. Kxh3 (30. Kh1 Rxf3 31. Ng1 Rd3 $17) 30... Qg4+ 31. Kg2 Qxf3+ 32. Kg1 h4 33. Nh1 Qe3+ { end of game } 34. Kg2 (34. Nf2 Qxf2+ 35. Kh1 h3 36. Qf1 Qxf1+ 37. Rxf1 Rxf1+ 38. Ng1 Re8 39. a3 Ree1 40. a4 Rxg1#) 34... h3# { 0-1 Black wins by checkmate. } 0-1


