1. e4 d6 2. d4 Nf6 3. Nc3 g6 4. f4 Bg7 5. Nf3 O-O 6. e5 { B09 Pirc Defense: Austrian Attack, Unzicker Attack } 6... dxe5 7. fxe5 Nd5 8. Bc4 Nb6 9. Bb3 c5 10. O-O?! { (0.69 → -0.23) Inaccuracy. dxc5 was best. } (10. dxc5 Qxd1+ 11. Nxd1 N6d7 12. e6 Nxc5 13. exf7+ Kh8 14. Bc4 Nc6 15. Be3 Be6 16. Bxe6 Nxe6) 10... cxd4 11. Ne4 Nc6 12. Qe1 Bf5?! { (-0.62 → 0.30) Inaccuracy. Be6 was best. } (12... Be6 13. Bxe6 fxe6 14. Qh4 h5 15. Bg5 Qd5 16. Rae1 Rae8 17. b3 Nxe5 18. Nxe5 Rxf1+ 19. Rxf1) 13. Qh4 Bxe4?? { (0.05 → 2.38) Blunder. h5 was best. } (13... h5 14. Ng3 Be6 15. Bxe6 fxe6 16. Qe4 Qe8 17. Bd2 Nd7 18. Ng5 Rxf1+ 19. Rxf1 Nc5 20. Qe2) 14. Qxe4?? { (2.38 → -1.04) Blunder. Ng5 was best. } (14. Ng5 h5) 14... e6 15. Bg5 Qc7 16. Rae1?! { (-0.83 → -1.69) Inaccuracy. Bf6 was best. } (16. Bf6 Nd7) 16... h6?? { (-1.69 → 0.94) Blunder. Nd7 was best. } (16... Nd7 17. Nxd4) 17. Bf6?? { (0.94 → -1.07) Blunder. Qh4 was best. } (17. Qh4 Kh7) 17... Bxf6?? { (-1.07 → 5.02) Blunder. a5 was best. } (17... a5) 18. exf6 Nd7 19. Bxe6?! { (5.07 → 3.82) Inaccuracy. Qh4 was best. } (19. Qh4) 19... Kh7? { (3.82 → 6.83) Mistake. Nce5 was best. } (19... Nce5 20. Nxe5) 20. Qh4 Nxf6 21. Bxf7 Kg7 22. Nxd4?? { (9.38 → 2.87) Blunder. Qxf6+ was best. } (22. Qxf6+ Kxf6 23. Nxd4+ Kg7 24. Ne6+ Kh8 25. Nxc7 Rac8 26. Ne6 Rfe8 27. Bxe8 Rxe8 28. Rf6 Nd4) 22... Qxf7 23. Ne6+ Kg8 24. Nxf8 Rxf8 25. Qxh6 Qg7 26. Qxg7+?! { (2.93 → 1.79) Inaccuracy. Qg5 was best. } (26. Qg5) 26... Kxg7 27. Re6 Rf7 28. c3 Nd8 29. Re2 Nc6 30. Ref2 g5 31. h3 Ne5?? { (1.91 → 4.28) Blunder. Kg6 was best. } (31... Kg6) 32. Rf5 Ned7 33. Rxg5+ Kh6 34. Rgf5 Kg6 35. g4 Re7 36. Kg2 Nd5? { (4.26 → 9.04) Mistake. b6 was best. } (36... b6 37. h4) 37. Rxd5 { Black resigns. } 1-0


