1. e4 d6 2. d4 Nf6 3. Nc3 g6 4. Nf3 Bg7 5. h3 O-O 6. Be3 c6 7. a4 Nbd7 8. a5 e5 9. dxe5 dxe5 10. Qd6 Ne8 11. Qd2 { Qb4 is interesting } 11... Qe7 (11... Nef6 12. Qd6 Ne8 13. Qb4 Bf6 14. Bc4 Be7 15. Qa4 Nc5 16. Qa2 $16) 12. Bc4 Nc5 13. b4 Ne6 { big mistake } (13... Nd7 { keeps control of c5 square } 14. Rb1 b5 15. axb6 axb6 (15... Nxb6 16. Bc5 $16) 16. O-O b5 17. Bb3 Nc7 (17... Qxb4 18. Bxf7+ Rxf7 19. Rxb4 $16) 18. Rfd1 Ne6 19. Qd6 $16) 14. Bxe6 { giving opponent the bishop pair but winning exchange immediately } { [%cal Gc4e6,Ge3c5,Gc5f8] } 14... Bxe6 (14... Qxe6 15. Bc5 Nc7 16. Bxf8 $16) 15. Bc5 Qc7 { [%csl Ga7,Gb4,Ga5][%cal Gc5f8,Ge1g1] } 16. O-O { most accurate - not tempted to take rook } (16. Bxf8 Bxf8 17. O-O Rd8 18. Qe3 Bxb4 19. Na4 Bxa5 (19... c5 20. Nc3 Bxa5 21. Nxe5 Bb4 22. Nf3 $16) 20. Qxa7 $16) 16... Rd8 17. Qe3 Nd6 18. Bxa7 { threat Bb6 } { [%csl Gb4,Ga5,Gb6][%cal Ga7b6] } 18... Nc4 19. Qe2 b6 (19... Bh6 20. Bc5 Rfe8 21. Rfb1 $16) 20. Ng5 (20. axb6 Nxb6 21. Qa6 Nc4 22. Ng5 Qe7 23. h4 Rfe8 24. Bc5 Qd7 25. Rfd1 Qc8 26. Rxd8 Rxd8 27. Nxe6 Qxe6 28. b5 cxb5 29. Qxb5 $16) 20... Bc8 (20... Qxa7 21. Nxe6 fxe6 22. Qxc4 bxa5 23. bxa5 $16) 21. Qxc4 Qxa7 22. Qxc6 bxa5 23. Nd5 { two knights vs two bishops } 23... Bd7 (23... Qb7 24. Nf6+ (24. Rfd1 Qxc6 (24... axb4 25. Qxb7 Bxb7 26. Ne7+ Kh8 27. Nxf7+ Rxf7 28. Rxd8+ Bf8 29. Nd5 $16) 25. Ne7+ Kh8 26. Nxf7+ (26. Nxc6 Rxd1+ 27. Rxd1 axb4 28. Rd8 Rxd8 29. Nxf7+ Kg8 30. Nfxd8 $16) 26... Rxf7 27. Rxd8+ Rf8 28. Nxc6 $16) 24... Bxf6 25. Qxf6 axb4 $10) 24. Nf6+ Bxf6 (24... Kh8 25. Nxd7 Rxd7 26. Rxa5 Qb7 27. Qxb7 Rxb7 28. Rb1 $16) 25. Qxf6 a4 26. Nxf7 { end of game } 26... a3 (26... Rxf7 27. Qxd8+ Kg7 28. c4 Qb7 29. Rfd1 Qa7 (29... h6 30. Rd6 Bxh3 31. gxh3 Qxb4 32. Qb6 $16) 30. Qh4 Qc7 31. Qg5 Qxc4 32. Qxe5+ Kh6 33. Qb2 Qxe4 34. Rd4 $16) (26... h5 27. Qxg6#) 27. Nh6# { 1-0 White wins by checkmate. } 1-0


